        <item>
            <title>1.6.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 13:27:53 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>16</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.6.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.6.0</h2>
<p>Bills that change every month: Otto asks what a bill actually cost when you pay it, keeps the real history, and estimates next month. And the globe button now opens the biller's website inside Otto — log in yourself, and Otto reads the new amount off the page for a one-click update. Otto still never pays anything.</p>
]]></description>
